      <title>分析师称日本央行结果对日元影响喜忧参半，焦点目前转向美联储</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/boj-outcome-mixed-for-yen-focus-now-turns-to-fed-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师和策略师表示，日本央行加息并削减债券购买量后，日元大幅波动，因为会议结果并未真正明确央行的长期路径。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/boj-outcome-mixed-for-yen-focus-now-turns-to-fed-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:26:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士央行公布半年盈利，因股市强劲抵消瑞郎升值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/snb-reports-half-year-profit-as-strong-stocks-offset-franc-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士央行因股市和金价上涨而获得了六个月的稳健盈利，补充了其资本基础，并让人们继续希望央行能够恢复向政府支付款项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/snb-reports-half-year-profit-as-strong-stocks-offset-franc-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:20:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
